00:20:36,583 --> 00:20:39,083
Would you like to
help out with the plans?

495
00:20:39,166 --> 00:20:40,916
[KYON]
Sure. I'm happy to.

496
00:20:46,291 --> 00:20:48,250
[KYON]
Hm...

497
00:20:48,333 --> 00:20:49,666
Well, first of all,

498
00:20:49,750 --> 00:20:52,041
no scattering snow in the
clubroom. It'll just melt.

499
00:20:52,125 --> 00:20:53,375
[NAGATO sighs]

500
00:20:53,458 --> 00:20:54,666
--As for the cake...
--[NAGATO] Just four tiers?

501
00:20:54,750 --> 00:20:55,958
That's like a wedding cake!

502
00:20:56,041 --> 00:20:58,125
Wha-- Huh?

503
00:20:58,208 --> 00:20:59,208
--W-Wait! Wedding?

504
00:20:59,291 --> 00:21:00,541
--Fine. Two tiers.
--W-Wait! Wedding?

505
00:21:00,625 --> 00:21:02,125
--But that's the absolute most.
--W-Wait! Wedding?

506
00:21:02,208 --> 00:21:04,375
[KYON]
Now about this dress.

507
00:21:04,458 --> 00:21:05,166
[NAGATO]
I want pure white!

508
00:21:05,250 --> 00:21:06,416
It's a wedding dress!

509
00:21:06,500 --> 00:21:07,750
It's not!

510
00:21:07,833 --> 00:21:10,166
Maybe we should just table
the dress for now, okay?

511
00:21:10,250 --> 00:21:11,166
[NAGATO]
Mm-hm.

512
00:21:11,250 --> 00:21:12,208
Hey, you guys!

513
00:21:12,291 --> 00:21:13,291
Hey, Asakura.

514
00:21:13,375 --> 00:21:15,541
[KYON]
You're late. Where've you been?

515
00:21:15,625 --> 00:21:18,416
[ASAKURA giggles]

516
00:21:18,500 --> 00:21:20,166
How do you like them apples?

517
00:21:20,250 --> 00:21:21,625
[KYON]
No way!

518
00:21:21,708 --> 00:21:23,666
[ASAKURA] It says we can use
the clubroom on Christmas.

519
00:21:23,750 --> 00:21:25,625
I just kept bugging
them until they caved.

520
00:21:25,708 --> 00:21:26,875
I thought we were just gonna

521
00:21:26,958 --> 00:21:29,625
have to sneak in here
after hours. Good job!

522
00:21:29,708 --> 00:21:32,833
Well, being an honor student
does open some doors.

523
00:21:32,916 --> 00:21:37,083
Now that it's official,
I think that we can go all-out.

524
00:21:37,166 --> 00:21:39,875
So, what have you guys
been up to today?

525
00:21:39,958 --> 00:21:42,375
We're trying to hash
out party decorations.

526
00:21:42,458 --> 00:21:44,708
Yeah? What do you have so far?

527
00:21:46,166 --> 00:21:47,916
[ASAKURA]
Oh?

528
00:21:48,000 --> 00:21:49,208
So, what do you think?

529
00:21:49,291 --> 00:21:52,625
[ASAKURA] Hm... I think
these look pretty good.

530
00:21:52,708 --> 00:21:54,125
Seriously?

531
00:21:54,208 --> 00:21:57,166
Well, there might be one or two
suggestions I would make.

532
00:21:57,250 --> 00:21:59,666
But I know Nagato's been
working really hard on this,

533
00:21:59,750 --> 00:22:01,791
and I wouldn't wanna
seem too controlling.

534
00:22:01,875 --> 00:22:03,125
Huh?

535
00:22:03,208 --> 00:22:04,541
Hey!

536
00:22:04,625 --> 00:22:06,458
If you have something to say,
I think now's the time.

537
00:22:06,541 --> 00:22:08,666
[ASAKURA]
Oh yeah? Well...

538
00:22:08,750 --> 00:22:10,083
A cake with four tiers?

539
00:22:10,166 --> 00:22:12,083
[KYON] I was able to
get it down to two.

540
00:22:12,166 --> 00:22:13,916
[ASAKURA]
And the snow in the clubroom?

541
00:22:14,000 --> 00:22:15,166
[KYON]
"Yuki" means snow, right?

542
00:22:15,250 --> 00:22:16,333
[ASAKURA]
Huh?

543
00:22:16,416 --> 00:22:17,583
[KYON] That's why she's
always so chilly!

544
00:22:17,666 --> 00:22:18,833
[ASAKURA] Do you know
how bad that joke was?

545
00:22:18,916 --> 00:22:19,916
[KYON]
It wasn't that bad.

546
00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:21,291
[ASAKURA]
Awful.

547
00:22:21,375 --> 00:22:24,000
[NAGATO] It'll be fun.
I'll make it a good party.

548
00:22:24,083 --> 00:22:27,291
And when I do, maybe...

549
00:22:27,375 --> 00:22:29,208
[KYON]
Hey there. Let me help you.

550
00:22:29,291 --> 00:22:30,791
Here, gimme that book.

551
00:22:30,875 --> 00:22:32,500
You want a library card, right?

552
00:22:32,583 --> 00:22:34,500
I'll go take care of it for you.

553
00:22:39,708 --> 00:22:41,000
[NAGATO]
Ah--

554
00:22:45,625 --> 00:22:46,250
[KYON]
Hey. Nagato.

555
00:22:46,333 --> 00:22:48,250
Huh?

556
00:22:48,333 --> 00:22:50,625
Don't worry. The
party'll be great.

557
00:22:50,708 --> 00:22:54,541
[gasps] Yep!

558
00:22:54,625 --> 00:22:57,166
[NAGATO]
And maybe... I'll tell him...

559
00:22:57,250 --> 00:22:59,416
...how I feel about him.

560
00:24:34,416 --> 00:24:37,708
[NAGATO] Next episode:
"Joy to the World."

